title: DDFP 447:  All-time NFL Draft of 2016 Picks 16-20 & 2016 NFL Schedule
itunes:title: DDFP 447:  All-time NFL Draft of 2016 Picks 16-20 & 2016 NFL Schedule
description:
Shek sits down with Handsome Hank as they discuss the Rams trading with the Titans for the No.1 pick and the 2016 NFL Schedule Release. Then, NFL Network’s Shaun O’Hara joins Shek and Handsome Hank to break down picks 16-20 of the All-Time Draft of 2016.
